Sync-before-emit (rs-codeinsight + rs-search): outputs must come from freshly-completed indices. Cache serves ONLY on digest match (mtime sum + git HEAD + dirty-tree marker). Default invocation runs fresh. --read-cache permitted only when .codeinsight.digest matches; mismatch auto-refreshes. rs-search runs scan + embed + sweep before first result, emits [index fully synced: ...]. Unverified-index emit = stale ground truth - never emit codeinsight/search output from an index not freshly synced this invocation.